		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Man with all the powerful tools we have nowadays, we don't have much excuse for not developing quality games of our own.  The development teams weren't near as big as I would have previously thought.  It does present a stumbling block if a coder can't draw, but at least you don't have to be able to write music.  It would probably help to have making games as your day job, but who needs sleep anyways?

		

		</td>
